      "comment": "A label that describes the accessibility score of a location. The first argument is the score. The second argument is the maximum score. The third argument is the quality of the score. The fourth argument is the string “Excellent”, the string “Good”, the string “Fair”, the string “Poor”, or the string “Very Poor”.",
